com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.fru

Class ReadFruDataResponseData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.fru.ReadFruDataResponseData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResponseData

    public class ReadFruDataResponseData
extends java.lang.Object
implements ResponseData
    Wrapper for Read FRU Data response. Contains only raw data, because size of the FRU Inventory Area might exceed size of the communication packet so it might come in many ReadFruDataResponseData packets and it must be decoded by ReadFruData.decodeFruData(java.util.List).
